summary: Contains a skull throne model made of purely vanilla assets.
descriptionHtml:
I put this together after it was requested on r/skyrimmods.

The archive contains only the model (since it's all vanilla assets, it will use either vanilla textures or any replacer you have installed). It [i]should [/i]be ready to be used in the Creation Kit (fully prepared in NifSkope), but it's the first furniture object I've done, so I'm not entirely sure. If there's a problem with it, tell me and I'll do my best to fix it!

As long as you credit me, you're free to use this for whatever project you like.
Please do not upload this anywhere else.
author: Cyphe
